version_description: I can't take credit for determining what chords were used. I took the chords straight from a youtube video where this song's writer, Jeff Lynne, tells the viewer the exact chords used. View youtube video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O0mYVP4zR5s.
Complete chords and tab for the melody / original key and suggestion for capo 3rd fret / https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9JXugX4wZ3U.
Complete lyrics and chords / thoroughly ear-transcribed / suggestions for voicings of special chords.
Complete and well-aligned chord sheet / intermediate with split chords and suggestions for playable voicings.
Complete lyrics and chords / short tab for the riff / https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sErqZGhMZ7g.
Well-aligned chords for all parts of the song / intermediate version featuring slash chords / suggestions for playable voicings.
I finally completed it... so enjoy playing :).
